data.description: Don't miss this opportunity to own a spectacular home with a large backyard, a two-car garage, and three spacious bedrooms in a highly desirable neighborhood. In addition to the incredible features of this home, the community itself has so much to offer. Take a stroll through the impeccably maintained common areas, unwind by the sparkling pool on hot summer days, or socialize with friendly neighbors at community events. Come see and experience the charm of this exceptional property.Assumable FHA 3.25% loan.
